data.description: Luxury Living at its Finest! This remarkable custom home nestled on a sprawling half-acre lot boasts unparalleled elegance. From the moment you step through the front door, you'll be captivated by the sheer perfection of every detail and the long lake view.  The expansive great room is accentuated by soaring ceilings and connects the living area, dining space, & a gourmet chef's kitchen with wall oven, range hood & wine fridge. Embrace the indoor-outdoor lifestyle as large triple sliders reveal a breathtaking oasis. Three outdoor living spaces await, each offering a distinct ambiance for relaxation and entertainment. The owner's suite offers his & her closets, and an en-suite bathroom with custom tile and separate vanities. Two additional suites provide luxurious accommodations, each with a walk-in closet and private bathroom. The spacious den/office/flex room, situated off the great room, offers endless possibilities and adapts effortlessly to your needs.  Beyond the confines of this impeccable residence lies the exclusive gated community of Kismet Lakes, where just 27 homes share in the allure of this pristine setting.  Don't miss your chance to experience absolute perfection.
